Shadow Hand (Strike)
Level: Swordsage 6, Saint 6
Initiation Action: 1 full-round action
Range: Melee attack
Target: One creature

When you initiate this maneuver, if your target can neither see nor hear you, your attack deals an extra 6d6 damage.  If your target is aware of the impending attack this strike only deals an extra 2d6 of damage.